CHANGING LOGO NAME RUGGED BOARD A5D2X:
======================================

->Install figlet(sudo apt-get install figlet)
->Give figlet NAME in terminal and give any name what you want to add.
->Copy that displayed name from the terminal.
->goto rugged terminal.
->goto etc folder (cd /etc/)
->In etc goto issue (vi issue)
->Paste that copied name.
->And then goto ssh (cd /etc/ssh/).
->In ssh goto sshd_config (vi sshd_config).
->And uncomment that #Banner /etc/issue/.
->save and cd.
->And reboot.
